{"tid":97143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友個朋友死左","createTime":"2017-01-27T12:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T14:52:19.000Z","uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edb321b4a1134d6c9f3970e2c7f3780e7ec31d99","tid":97143,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"朋友個朋友<br />\n我剩係見過一次<br />\n因佢之前咁岩一齊去op<br />\n佢男朋友都有黎<br />\n<br />\n琴日<br />\n朋友個朋友<br />\n好似飲醉酒咁揸左車黎<br />\n一落車好係咁笑<br />\n又企唔穩<br />\n之後一齊上朋友屋企玩<br />\n<br />\n上到去<br />\n佢入左房<br />\n之後我哋其他人喺廳玩<br />\n過左一粒鐘<br />\n佢男朋睇下佢做咩<br />\n入左房<br />\n咁我哋其他人冇理<br />\n<br />\n又過左排<br />\n我哋發覺佢倆個冇黎聲氣<br />\n就開門入房<br />\n發現倆個都自殺死咗<br />\n<br />\n首先係個女仔唔知咩事<br />\n好傷心自殺<br />\n之後佢男朋友原來入去已經見佢死咗<br />\n但就唔出聲<br />\n傷心到又自殺埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解我咁清楚？<br />\n我都唔知點解<br />\n但就有好強烈嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n之後<br />\n我就醒咗。。<br />\n但今朝到依家都覺得個夢好真實<br />\n好寒<br />\n我真係見過個女仔<br />\n<br />\n希望佢生活事事順利<br />\n開開心心<br />\n千祈唔好有事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21dadb3b255aa6fc81c88ccd7aa8c14ffa022f29","tid":97143,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67756d3c3892ad5273b4ba153c15f7a4f5abbf61","tid":97143,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老芬<br />\n你覺得點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0212f7e2f5ea6ab7c9f32bf8dec09ff16c9219d","tid":97143,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"又要話保佑人平平安安<br />\n個標題又實牙實齒話人死左<br />\n想點呀大佬"},{"pid":"61215032a3cd230295461c8d43294f9110df3521","tid":97143,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:34:13.0